#: ../../build123d/docs/tutorial_selectors.rst:49
msgid "The next set of features in this design will be created on the top of the cylinder and be described by a planar sketch (:class:`~build_sketch.BuildSketch` is the tool for drawing on planar surfaces) , so we'll create a sketch centered on the top of the cylinder.  To locate this sketch we'll use the cylinder's top Face as shown here:"
